<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Successful | Arzani Marketplace</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .success-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .success-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            color: #28a745;
        }

        .subscription-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .subscription-label {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .subscription-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #041b76;
            border-color: #041b76;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #052287;
            border-color: #052287;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(4, 27, 118, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-outline-secondary {
            color: #041b76;
            border-color: #041b76;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-outline-secondary:hover {
            background-color: rgba(4, 27, 118, 0.1);
            color: #041b76;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .buttons-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .buttons-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8">
                <div class="success-container">
                    <svg class="success-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M12 22C17.5228 22 22 17.5228 22 12C22 6.47715 17.5228 2 12 2C6.47715 2 2 6.47715 2 12C2 17.5228 6.47715 22 12 22Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                        <path d="M8 12L10.5 14.5L16 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                    
                    <h1 class="display-6 mb-3">Subscription Successful!</h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4">
                        Thank you for subscribing to our <%= planName %> plan. Your account has been upgraded and you now have access to all the premium features.
                    </p>

                    <div class="subscription-details">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-sm-6">
                                <div class="subscription-label">Plan</div>
                                <div class="subscription-value"><%= planName %></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-6">
                                <div class="subscription-label">Status</div>
                                <div class="subscription-value">Active</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-6">
                                <div class="subscription-label">Billing Cycle</div>
                                <div class="subscription-value">Monthly</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-sm-6">
                                <div class="subscription-label">Next Billing Date</div>
                                <div class="subscription-value"><%= nextBillingDate %></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
                        <strong>Tip:</strong> You can manage your subscription at any time from your account profile.
                    </div>

                    <div class="buttons-container">
                        <a href="/marketplace" class="btn btn-primary">Start Exploring</a>
                        <a href="/profile" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">View Profile</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
